What is the best overall team composition to handle any level?  I 
currently use 3 of every type but Thief (I just sent my registration 
money in the mail today).

I have a difficult time getting through the level with Tic and Tac in 
it without characters dying.  The only way I beat that level without 
losing any characters is if all my characters act as a team instead
of 
 individual efforts.  Does the registered work on getting your team
to 
 work as a team 100% of the time?  I would have to say Tic and Tac is 
the hardest level next to the last level.  Is it underrated as 
moderate?
